[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0632","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0632.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0394","title":"DPEC Courseware Web Server 任意用户密码修改漏洞","description":"DPEC Courseware Web Server 存在密码修改漏洞，远程攻击者可在无需知道原始密码的情况下，直接修改其他用户的账户密码。该漏洞影响 DPEC Online Courseware 系统，攻击者利用此漏洞可获取其他用户的账户控制权，进而访问课程资料或执行未授权操作。由于无需身份认证即可利用，危害等级严重，CVSS 评分 10.0。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0394"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:18.173","remediation":"立即停用 DPEC Online Courseware 并迁移至其他受支持的在线课程平台；如无法立即替换，应在 Web 服务器层面通过 ACL 限制管理后台访问 IP 范围，并禁用密码修改功能涉及的 CGI 脚本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91651770630788&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6df16fc0c02ccadd2d0fbb0029e3db345d75f1c8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0394.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0394","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0394.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ec31d5593e31331ed2058e001803e087d65aa416/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0394.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2wqv-jwmj-rrvv/GHSA-2wqv-jwmj-rrvv.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0394.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/565/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000425.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a621bf71-a318-4813-9d54-b3d23b540b4c.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0632.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0632.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0632.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0630","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0630.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0393","title":"Eric Allman Sendmail 头扫描拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sendmail 8.8.x 及 8.9.2 版本在处理邮件头时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标邮件服务器发送包含大量邮件头的特制邮件消息，触发 Sendmail 的邮件头预扫描（headers prescan）过程消耗过度资源，导致服务崩溃或无法响应正常请求，造成拒绝服务。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0393"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:18.040","remediation":"升级至 Sendmail 8.9.3 或更高版本，该版本修复了 headers prescan 处理逻辑中的缺陷。若无法升级，可在 sendmail.cf 中限制每个邮件的最大头部数量（MaxHeadersLength 参数），并在 MTA 层面配置 rate limiting 限制单连接请求频率以缓解 DoS 攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91694391227372&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/23167","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0393.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0393","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0393.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0393.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-34q2-7xrv-pfcm/GHSA-34q2-7xrv-pfcm.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/sendmail_parsing_redirection.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0393.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0630.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0622","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0622.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0388","title":"DataLynx suGuard 1.0 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"DataLynx suGuard 1.0 存在本地权限提升漏洞。该程序在执行 ps 命令时信任 PATH 环境变量，未对程序路径进行绝对路径引用，导致本地攻击者可通过修改 PATH 环境变量将恶意程序替换为 ps，从而以 root 权限执行任意命令。攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限，利用难度较低，危害较高。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0388"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:17.403","remediation":"将 suGuard 中对 ps 命令的调用路径从相对路径改为绝对路径（如 /bin/ps 或 /usr/bin/ps），或在执行前将 PATH 环境变量重置为安全值（如 /bin:/usr/bin），防止攻击者通过篡改 PATH 劫持命令执行。建议立即停止使用已停止维护的 DataLynx suGuard，迁移到持续更新的替代方案（如 sudo 或 doas）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/3186","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19146","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0388.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0388","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0388.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85e