,"remediation":"升级到 LaserFiche 现代版本（如 9.0 以上）以使用加密存储和审计日志功能；若无法升级，迁移至 Hyland 或其他具备加密存储与操作审计的文档管理平台。作为临时缓解措施，在网络层限制对 LaserFiche 服务的访问来源，仅允许受信任管理 IP 连接，并在 NetWare 服务器上启用文件系统和操作审计日志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0361","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0361.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0361","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0361.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0361.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7ch8-6pch-qhqg/GHSA-7ch8-6pch-qhqg.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0361.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82496/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000420.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--106f99f3-e05b-4e49-be82-91767e97aac7.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0592.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0586","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0586.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0355","title":"CA ControlIT 4.5 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"