/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0255","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0255.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0255.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0255.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3phx-q7wc-mf8g/GHSA-3phx-q7wc-mf8g.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0255.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--0ec05ae5-953f-4811-908d-245d2cf1e5af.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0440.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0433","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0433.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0248","title":"SSH sshd 认证代理竞争条件漏洞","description":"SSH 服务软件 sshd 1.2.17 版本的身份认证代理机制存在竞争条件漏洞（Race Condition）。远程攻击者在认证窗口内利用时序差向目标发送精心构造的认证请求，可在合法用户完成认证前截获或替换其身份凭证，从而窃取其他用户的 SSH 登录凭据并获得未授权访问。该漏洞影响早期 SSH 协议实现，利用难度较低，可导致敏感信息泄露和系统被控。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0248"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.860","remediation":"升级至 sshd 1.2.18 及以上版本，该版本已修复认证代理机制中的条件竞争漏洞。也可迁移至 OpenSSH（自 1999 年起开源维护），并保持版本更新。若无法升级，限制对 ssh-agent 的本地访问权限，仅允许受信任用户使用代理转发功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://oliver.efri.hr/~crv/security/bugs/mUNIXes/ssh2.html","http://www.uni-karlsruhe.de/~ig25/ssh-faq/ssh-faq-6.html#ss6.1","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0248.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0248.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0248","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0248.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0248.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0248.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vhcr-j22h-735c/GHSA-vhcr-j22h-735c.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82092/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0248.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0433.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0428","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0428.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0243","title":"Linux cfingerd 远程权限提升漏洞","description":"Linux cfingerd（可配置的 Finger 服务守护进程）存在远程权限提升漏洞，未经身份认证的攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的 Finger 请求触发该漏洞，成功利用后可获取目标系统 root 最高权限，完全控制受影响服务器。该漏洞影响多个 Linux 发行版中运行的 cfingerd 服务，攻击者无需任何认证即可远程发起攻击，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0243"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.250","remediation":"立即停止并卸载 cfingerd 服务（`systemctl stop cfingerd && apt-get remove cfingerd` 或 `yum remove cfingerd`）。cfingerd 已在 2000 年代初停止维护，不存在补丁修复。建议在 iptables 或防火墙中封禁 TCP 端口 79，同时禁用 finger 协议。改用现代认证机制（如 LDAP/SSSD）替代 finger 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.geocrawler.com/archives/3/92/1996/9/0/2217716/","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0243.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0243","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0243.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0243.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0243.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q27j-g75f-h573/GHSA-q27j-g75f-h573.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/cfinger_format_bug.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80889/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0243.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0428.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0425","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0425.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0240","title":"防火墙或过滤器 IP分片SYN数据包 安全策略绕过漏洞","description":"部分防火墙或网络过滤器在处理分片 SYN 数据包时存在策略绕过漏洞，攻击者可通过向目标网络发送设置了 IP 保留位的特制分片 SYN 数据包，绕过防火墙或过滤器的访问控制规则，未经授权访问受保护的内部网络资源。该漏洞影响多种品牌和型号的防火墙产品，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。厂商通过更新防火墙的分片重组和标志位检查逻辑修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0240"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:58.897","remediation":"对防火墙启用状态检测（Stateful Inspection）功能，确保所有IP分片报文在重组完成后再进行规则匹配，禁止直接放行分片SYN包。同时在防火墙上配置策略丢弃IP头部保留位非零的数据包，并禁用非必要接口的IP路由转发功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0240","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0240.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0240","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0240.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0240.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0240.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9w2q-p353-cvp5/GHSA-9w2q-p353-cvp5.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0240.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0425.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0416","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0416.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0231","title":"IP-Switch IMail 和 Seattle Labs Slmail 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"IP-Switch IMail 与 Seattle Labs Slmail 2.6 邮件服务软件中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 SMTP 服务发送超长 VRFY 命令参数触发栈缓冲区溢出，导致服务拒绝服务，在特定条件下可进一步实现远程代码执行。该漏洞影响上述邮件系统的 SMTP 组件，利用无需认证，攻击门槛较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0231"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.770","remediation":"该漏洞存在于 SLMail 2.6 及更早版本的 VRFY 命令处理中，超长参数导致栈缓冲区溢出。厂商后续版本已修复此问题，建议尽快升级至 SLMail 3.0 及以上版本，或迁移至 Ipswitch IMail 最新版本。若无法立即升级，应在 SMTP 代理或 IPS 设备上限制 VRFY 命令参数长度不超过 256 字节，并禁用 VRFY/EXPN 命令以降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0231","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0231.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0231","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0231.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0231.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0231.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5r6m-8793-wrhh/GHSA-5r6m-8793-wrhh.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/resul